description.narrative: Regular monitoring was undertaken for the turnaround time for all 4 categories. The average turnaround was generally met for institutional services. For the other 3 categories, the average turnaround time was higher. Hence, a bottleneck analysis has been undertaken and main reasons for delays have been identified. S&P will be working with program/requesting sections to address the bottlenecks. | Status:Constrained | As-of Date:09/01/2022
